# Shared Rules from ai-general-tools

When working in this project, apply the rules from the shared `.claude` config:

**Location:** `../ai-general-tools/.claude/rules/` (or `.claude/rules/` via symlink)

**Rule files to consider:**
- `development-rules.md` – Development workflow and standards
- `primary-workflow.md` – Primary workflow patterns
- `documentation-management.md` – Documentation practices
- `team-coordination-rules.md` – Team coordination
- `orchestration-protocol.md` – Orchestration patterns

Read and apply these rules when relevant to the task at hand.
